<br>
I hope you have a bunch of pp saved. The price of a 6wis ring is about 200pp the velium 7wis about 1000pp. What you are asking can be very costly. I would suggest that you look at 3 different earings:<br>
<br>
1) Orc Fang(3ac 3str 15hp) about 75pp or more<br>
2) Cougar Claw(4AC 3Str 2Dex) about 200pp or more<br>
3) Forrest Loop(2AC 3Agi 3Dex 3Wis) about 400pp<br>
4) Sarnak Earing of Station(5ac 5str) Lore, Nodrop and very rare.<br>
<br>
For rings there are many choices. I still wear Jagged bands on a daily basis. They are cheap and the 5ac 3str is great bang for the buck. For palyer made rings that are good for Hybreds the plat or velium with Jade(AC, HP and mana) or Fire Opal(AC and HP).  The Diamond Wedding Band from the ToFS (+2 AC +3 Dexterity +5 Wisdom +5 Intelligence +8 Fire Resist +8 Cold Resist +15 Mana ) is about 2500pp. Its partner ring, the Rune Etched Wedding Band(+2 AC +3 Strength +4 Stamina +6 Agility +8 Posion Resist +8 Disease Resist +15 Hit Points ) is the same if not a little higher. It can get very expensive.<br>
<br>
As for SoW potions, they are available in 1, 5 and 10 dose stacks. Prices are usually 100 to 110pp for a 10 dose stack. I would ask Shamer or Baranea about these and they may do a little better for you.<br>
<br>
Regards,<br>
